org.concordia.kingdoms.board
Class Entry<T extends ICoordinate>

java.lang.Object
  org.concordia.kingdoms.board.Entry<T>

@AutoProperty
public class Entry<T extends ICoordinate>
extends Object

An Entry is a place holder for a Component. Each entry is recognized with its coordinate and the component. It's up to the client code to maintain the uniqueness of each entry.

Since:
1.0
Author:
Team K
